13:03.908 --> 13:08.746
♪ You asked me
how I was doing ♪

13:08.746 --> 13:11.541
♪ I said ♪

13:11.541 --> 13:14.085
♪ I'm okay ♪

13:18.298 --> 13:21.634
♪ Seconds go by ♪

13:21.634 --> 13:24.137
♪ Minutes pass ♪

13:32.186 --> 13:35.315
♪ Hours, they drag ♪

13:35.315 --> 13:38.318
♪ And days, they last ♪

13:41.821 --> 13:44.991
